{"tid":1928036,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林志偉被判即時入獄14天","createTime":"2020-03-16T07:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T07:48:50.000Z","uid":326897,"like":10,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"91e31338f498aca95f180582a62ca0ab64e29d63","tid":1928036,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:05:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514744-20200316.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514744-20200316.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebX9Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=57fc1da1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1514744-20200316.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fb22576d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1514744-20200316.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n男子盜酒精消毒劑判囚14天<br />\n2020-03-16 HKT 14:34<br />\n <br />\n一名47歲男子早前在荃灣一間藥妝店，偷取5支酒精消毒劑被捕，今日在觀塘裁判法院承認一項盜竊罪，被判即時入獄14天。<br />\n<br />\n有19次案底的被告<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">林志偉</span></span></strong>求情時稱，這些消毒劑是自用，但裁判官香淑嫻不相信。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，被告於本月14日在荃灣千色匯的一間藥妝店，偷取5支酒精消毒劑，共值225元。案情指，經理在被告的袋內找到未付款的5支消毒劑，報警求助，警員到場拘捕被告，被告在警誡下表示自己一時貪心下犯案。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幾時到黑狗林大總統呢</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6abf3ea296b2121485cf25269e00532bf4d25326","tid":1928036,"uid":113784,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:06:38.000Z","msg":"點解香港好似得幾個裁判官咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次都係呢個香淑嫻"},{"pid":"b1276a4bbaf2a8007ae0f29426565130962367f2","tid":1928036,"uid":204539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T07:07:57.000Z","msg":"林志偉其實駛唔駛返工<br />\n未見過佢著曱甴制服<br />\n喺現場會唔會見到佢<img src=\"/assets/fa